<p class="ql-align-center">你不带个十盒八盒月饼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都没有底气上高速</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201002/6bc1de9b45f249d499d95d05d94147bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没出门的各位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瓜子花生矿泉水通通拿出来吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《2020版双节大堵车》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马上就要激情上演了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201002/0bb21f94fa2245f1b71dd3245cd0bc85.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今年的国庆大堵车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比往常来得要早一些</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201002/dd9aa431b32a4118ba620d4326429957.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了不在高速上过双节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">9月29日那天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少人和领导磨破嘴皮子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才争取提前一天回家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万万没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遇上了一高速的聪明人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有他们的宠物狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201002/71a4e79686454828af90815095907c0b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201002/5235d3f9eac8492294b14057de6043e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201002/5e7130c17f2b4b0998380225f02c0904.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经堵了8小时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你们的月饼还剩几个</p>
