<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201002/cd761389f32f4c57aed7e6e2e3de5b66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我以为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再堵还能堵到天亮？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果…只是我以为</p>
