<p class="ql-align-center">有人斗起了地主</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201002/7a2487751b4c48cab18b2f690b414d89.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人打起了麻将</p>
